description: Fire Reports for all fire incidents occurring from 1/1/2011 through the previous month of the current year.  Data contains information from filed fire reports.  Included data covers the type of fire, location, cause of the fire, call received and incident response times, information on the property type and use for structure and mobile fires, estimated property loss incurred.  Also included in the data set are details on the structure involved and specifics on the range of fire and smoke damage for structure fires, data on the type/model of vehicle for mobile fires or estimate on the size of the affected area for outside fires.
title: Tacoma Fire Department - Fire Incident Data Table
